* Seeds should be created as nitro tasks:

```ts
// server/tasks/seed/posts.ts
export default defineTask({
  meta: {
      name: "seed:posts",
      description: "Seed Posts",
    },
  run({ payload, context }) {
    const db = useDb();
    // do seeding
    return { result: "Success" };
  },
});
```

Imports Needed for Interactive UI
```rust
use gpui::{
    InteractiveElement, // For .hover(), .cursor_pointer()
    MouseButton,        // For mouse event handling
    // ... other imports
};
```

- **对象结构完整性** - 确保对象字面量语法正确，字段位置准确
  ```typescript
  // ✅ 正确的对象结构
  console.log('调试信息:', {
    field1: value1,
    field2: value2,
    field3: value3  // 最后一个字段不需要逗号，但可以加上
  });

  // ❌ 错误的对象结构
  console.log('调试信息:', {
    field1: value1,
    field2: value2
  });
  field3: value3,  // 字段在对象外部，语法错误
  ```
